final_result.label: normal
final_result.response: Both options have their merits. A group message could create a sense of community and excitement about gathering, while reaching out to one friend at a time might feel more personal. How about considering what feels right for you? You could start with a group message to gauge interest, then follow up individually with those who respond. What do you think?
